WEBVTT

00:00.355 --> 00:02.355
Previously on
<i>Falling Skies...</i>

00:02.575 --> 00:04.521
The harness, is a process.

00:04.639 --> 00:06.493
And Ben isn't free from it.

00:06.522 --> 00:07.622
Looking for you family?

00:07.647 --> 00:09.590
I combed that
rubble for a long time...

00:09.615 --> 00:10.633
but they were gone.

00:10.658 --> 00:12.672
What were you and Jimmy doing
hunting Skitters, Ben?

00:12.697 --> 00:13.925
I need a reason?

00:13.950 --> 00:16.103
I'm sorry.
He's gone.

00:17.347 --> 00:18.235
You want out?

00:19.723 --> 00:20.720
There's the door.

00:21.636 --> 00:24.039
I can't protect them anymore.
We can't protect them anymore.

